  "body": "<p>One of my favorite new products for the Yes, Please collection is definitely <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/american-crafts/139088-lovely-yes-please-amy-tangerine-calendar-stamp-set/\">the calendar stamp</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600230115897-SL9SPCH3Q4YR2K2633L6/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>And it's in stock in limited quantities right now at <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/american-crafts/139088-lovely-yes-please-amy-tangerine-calendar-stamp-set/\">Two Peas In A Bucket</a> and <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=199868&amp;m=24698&amp;afftrack=calendar%20stamp&amp;urllink=www%2Esimonsaysstamp%2Ecom%2Fservlet%2Fthe%2D54210%2Fcalendar%2Dstamp%2Dset%2Dlovely%2FDetail\">Simon Says Stamp</a>. It was fun reading all your favorite techniques of the moment <a href=\"https://amy-tan-z6av.squarespace.com/amy-tangerine/2013/01/sc.html\">in this post</a>. </p><p><strong>The winner of the </strong><a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/shop/studio-selections--2/amy-tan-signature-series-autographed-copy?aff=6cc2c70f\"><strong>autographed copy of my book</strong></a><strong> is: #52 - Michelle Congrats!</strong></p>"
